children.title: Inclusion Criteria
children.description: All responses must be “Yes” unless specified as “NA”

children.title: Age >= 18 years
children.description: The age of the participant must be greater than 18.

children.title: a. Gastroesophageal reflux disease defined by diagnosis
children.description: Gastroesophageal reflux disease defined by diagnosis. ICD-9: 530.81, ICD-10: K21.9

children.title: b. GERD defined by drug, >= 3 months over 5 years
children.description: GERD defined by drug, duration of use >= 3 months over the last 5 years. Medication includes: omeprazole, esomeprazole, pantoprazole, rabeprazole, dexlansoprazole, lansoprazole, ranitidine, famotidine, cimetidine

children.title: c. GERD defined by prior endoscopic diagnosis of erosive esophagitis
children.description: GERD defined by prior endoscopic diagnosis of erosive esophagitis. ICD-9: 530.19, ICD-10: K21.0

children.title: Obesity (BMI>=30)
children.description: Obesity defined as body mass index greater than equal to 30.

children.title: Previous history of esophageal adenocarcinoma/cancer, esophageal squamous carcinoma
children.description: Previous history of esophageal adenocarcinoma/cancer, esophageal squamous carcinoma. ICD-9: 150.9, ICD-10: C15.9

children.title: Previous history of endoscopic ablation for Barrett's esophagus
children.description: Previous history of endoscopic ablation for Barrett's esophagus. CPT-4: 43229, 43270, 43228, 43258

children.title: Previous history of esophageal squamous dysplasia
children.description: Previous history of esophageal squamous dysplasia. ICD-9: 622.10, ICD-10: N87.9

children.title: Current Treatment (drug) with oral anticoagulation - warfarin
children.description: Current Treatment (drug) with oral anticoagulation - warfarin.

children.title: Current drug w/ Coumadin
children.description: Current Treatment (drug) with oral anticoagulation - Coumadin.

children.title: History of cirrhosis
children.description: History of cirrhosis. ICD-9: 571.5, ICD-10: K74.60

children.title: History of esophageal varices
children.description: History of esophageal varices. ICD-9: 456.20, ICD-10: I85.00

children.title: History of Barrett’s esophagus
children.description: History of Barrett’s esophagus. ICD-9: 530.85, ICD-10: K22.7, K22.710, K22.711, K22.719

children.title: History of endoscopy in the last 5 years
children.description: History of endoscopy in the last 5 years. CPT-4: 43235-43270
